<chapter xml:id="ch-comparing-multiple-groups" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Comparing Multiple Groups</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      This chapter extends group comparison to more than two groups using
      Analysis of Variance (ANOVA). You will learn how to test whether
      differences exist among multiple group means and how to follow up with
      post-hoc comparisons.
    </p>
